title: Never got Skin D:
body: I still have yet to get my skin the kale Skin D:. Help me rito :(((

replies.body: The gifts are still on the way, we're not done!  Bookmark our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)  for updates as there are a lot of accounts to gift.  Hang tight!
